{"tid":36838,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧琼：林鄭是「大政府」，曾俊華是「小政府」","createTime":"2016-12-13T03:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T04:03:24.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd575b00f634d719dc3220d4d22595cf9a0ba897","tid":36838,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2rSVa8S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2rSVa8S.jpg&h=6e259b34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民建聯主席李慧琼出席商台節目，再次表達對特首梁振英不角逐連任的驚訝，認為對方的行動一直表達爭取連任的意欲，但她指，梁十分顧家，相信家庭因素是不連任的重要考慮因素。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，民建聯仍未討論會支持誰人出選，她個人則認為本港的深層次矛盾一定要政府出手，但拒絕評論可能參選的人士。她指，據觀察，政務司長林鄭月娥相對是「大政府」，而財政司長曾俊華在處理經濟發展及財政資源上，傾向是「小政府」，但兩人現時仍未宣布參選，且未提出政綱，難說曾俊華一定是「小政府」而林鄭月娥亦未必是「大政府」。<br />\n<br />\n至於另一有意參選的新民黨葉劉淑儀，李慧琼表示，未能從對方於立法會的發言判斷是「大政府」還是「小政府」，認為要待葉劉淑儀發表政綱後才能評論。<br />\n<br />\n李慧琼續指，若2名司長一同參選，情況較罕有，又認為在備選期難有重大政策出台，相信待新一屆政府上場後，才會開展重大政策。<br />\n<br />\n對於林鄭月娥曾明確表示不參與特首選舉，但現時稱會積極考慮，李慧琼說，覺得林鄭月娥一直有心、有能力服務香港，對於她考慮選特首一事不感到驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161213/s00001/1481597566111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161213%2Fs00001%2F1481597566111&d=ZXOFqNCCuWIl91%2F%2FYo6SXhpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=40bc89ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161213%2Fs00001%2F1481597566111&h=28192074\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161213/s00001/1481597566111</a>"},{"pid":"b24f27be8881b0fcad0ab5e6cd5e07f6843f15c4","tid":36838,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf90834d659219c3aa152a8e9433acbe1f94ef3","tid":36838,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:30:02.000Z","msg":"葉劉是酸政府"},{"pid":"d012b239212d9425763335b2a171632aadf5c41d","tid":36838,"uid":322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:47:41.000Z","msg":"特區要做大政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反了反了"},{"pid":"204d61a29a00d558a03074baac4b58fce0fe38d0","tid":36838,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b0a2b551b6075d46e4eed7f471a4b992ef5e21","tid":36838,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:48:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>葉劉是酸政府</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫佢打道回府啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ca67ae82d5988ad4fa6cb049c1b41de2895d34","tid":36838,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T04:03:24.000Z","msg":"香港係一個獨立國家, 真係需要一個大政府"}]}